metadata.name: Underground S1 Access Pass (EXPIRES 6/30/23 - READ DESCRIPTION)
metadata.description:
IMPORTANT: Purchasing our Season 1 pass now will NO longer consider you for Season 2 whitelist (starting July 1st 2023).  We urge you to read our season 2 announcement on twitter and DM with any questions.

A private, members-only collective of 555 talented traders and investors looking to disrupt and define NFT culture. Membership to the organization and all benefits until June 30, 2023 come from holding the Underground S1 Access Pass NFT. Art created by toomuchlag.

Disclaimer: Shared accounts or mirroring our information to another server or community will result in an immediate ban and removal of your pass without refund or warning.
